
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hotel Security Services | ShieldWise Security</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #1a3c6e;
            --secondary-color: #bf9e5b;
            --text-color: #333333;
            --light-bg: #f8f9fa;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(26, 60, 110, 0.9), rgba(26, 60, 110, 0.9)), url('/img/hotel- ssecurity.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            padding: 150px 0;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .service-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .feature-list li {
            padding: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 30px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .feature-list li:before {
            content: 'âœ“';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .cta-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), #0d2b54);
            padding: 80px 0;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .btn-custom {
            background: var(--secondary-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-custom:hover {
            background: #a88b4a;
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .stat-card {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .testimonial {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../Partials/Header') %>

    <main>
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="hero-title">Hotel Security Services</h1>
                <p class="lead">Professional security solutions for hospitality establishments</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <section class="py-5">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                        <div class="service-card">
                            <h2 class="mb-4">Comprehensive Hotel Security Solutions</h2>
                            <p>At ShieldWise Security, we understand the unique security challenges faced by hotels and hospitality establishments. Our specialized hotel security services ensure the safety of guests, staff, and property while maintaining the welcoming atmosphere essential to the hospitality industry.</p>
                            
                            <h3 class="mt-4">Our Hotel Security Services Include:</h3>
                            <ul class="feature-list">
                                <li>24/7 Lobby and Entry Security</li>
                                <li>Guest Floor Patrols</li>
                                <li>Parking Structure Surveillance</li>
                                <li>Event Security for Hotel Functions</li>
                                <li>VIP Guest Protection</li>
                                <li>Security System Monitoring</li>
                                <li>Emergency Response Coordination</li>
                                <li>Lost and Found Management</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Statistics -->
                <div class="row mt-5">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="stat-card">
                            <div class="stat-number">100+</div>
                            <div>Hotels Protected</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="stat-card">
                            <div class="stat-number">24/7</div>
                            <div>Security Coverage</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="stat-card">
                            <div class="stat-number">15+</div>
                            <div>Years Experience</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Testimonials -->
                <div class="row mt-5">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="testimonial">
                            <p class="mb-3">"ShieldWise's hotel security team has significantly improved our guest safety and satisfaction. Their professional approach and attention to detail are outstanding."</p>
                            <strong>- Robert Chen</strong><br>
                            <small>General Manager, Grand Plaza Hotel</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="testimonial">
                            <p class="mb-3">"The level of service provided by ShieldWise's security officers has made a real difference in our hotel's safety and guest experience."</p>
                            <strong>- Sarah Johnson</strong><br>
                            <small>Operations Director, Luxury Bay Resort</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <section class="cta-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="mb-4">Secure Your Hotel Today</h2>
                <p class="mb-4">Contact us for a customized hotel security solution</p>
                <a href="/get-quote" class="btn btn-custom">Get a Free Quote</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('../Partials/Footer') %>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
